{"type": "email", "id": "email_001", "subject": "CARB 2035 ZEV Mandate Compliance Status", "from": "michael.williams@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Michael Williams", "to": ["sofia.rodriguez@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["jack.martin@elexionautomotive.com", "emily.johnson@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2022-05-01 10:00:00", "body": "Good Morning Sofia,

I hope this email finds you well. We've just completed our 2025 compliance review and I wanted to share our progress towards the CARB's 2035 100% ZEV mandate. As of now, Elexion Automotive covers around 60% of the new CARB ACC II mandate criteria.

Our development team is working diligently on the remaining 40% and we're confident that we'll be fully compliant by 2035, if not earlier. I'll keep you updated on our progress.

Best,
Michael Williams", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "Re: CARB 2035 ZEV Mandate Compliance Status", "from": "sofia.rodriguez@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Sofia Rodriguez", "to": ["michael.williams@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["jack.martin@elexionautomotive.com", "emily.johnson@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2022-05-01 11:15:00", "body": "Hi Michael,

Thank you for this update. It's great to hear that we're more than halfway towards meeting the CARB's 100% ZEV mandate. I look forward to further updates on our progress.

Best,
Sofia Rodriguez", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "Re: CARB 2035 ZEV Mandate Compliance Status", "from": "michael.williams@elexionautomotive.com", "from_name": "Michael Williams", "to": ["sofia.rodriguez@elexionautomotive.com"], "cc": ["jack.martin@elexionautomotive.com", "emily.johnson@elexionautomotive.com"], "date": "2022-05-01 11:30:00", "body": "Hi Sofia,

I'm glad you found the update helpful. Rest assured, our team is committed to making Elexion Automotive fully compliant with the CARB's 100% ZEV mandate by 2035. We'll continue to keep you posted on our progress.

Best,
Michael Williams", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
